Skill-initiated bootstrap contract (gm-plugkit lib/skill-bootstrap.js): bootstrapPlugkit(sessionId) performs wasm initialization for skill-driven dispatch without hook infrastructure. Accepts optional SESSION_ID, ensures the wasm artifact + plugkit-wasm-wrapper.js are in place, writes status/error to .gm/exec-spool/.bootstrap-status.json and .bootstrap-error.json for spool awareness, returns {ok:true} on success or {ok:false,error} on failure. Failures are non-fatal - callers fall back to a degraded surface.